Chandler Durham (amụrụ n'August 9, 1994), nke a maara dị ka Turbo, bụ ónyé America na-emepụta ihe ndekọ na ónyé na-ede egwu. A maara ya nke ọma màkà mmepụta ya na Young Thug, Travis Scott, Gunna, Nav, na Lil Baby.
Ọ bụ ónyé isi mepụtara abọm studio mbụ nke Gunna Drip ma ọ bụ Drown 2 ya na ónyé na-emepụta ihe ndekọ Wheezy. Abọm ahụ malitere na No
1 na chaatị Billboard Top R&B / Hip-Hop Albums.

N'afọ 2017, Turbo mepụtara ọtụtụ egwu na We Want Smoke, abọm nchịkọta nke ndị na-ese ihe bịanyere aka na T.I.'s Grand Hustle Records. Ọ bụ ónyé isi mepụtara Drip Harder, mixtape jikọrọ aka nke Gunna na Lil Baby wepụtara na 2018, ọ bụkwa ónyé na-emepụta egwu anọ nke mixtape ahụ, gụnyere "Never Recover" na "Close Friends" nke e nyèrè Platinum na "Drip Too Hard" nke e nwetara 3 × Platinum. O mepụtara "Slimed In" na album nchịkọta nke Young Thug Slime Language, nke e wepụtara na 2018. N'otu afọ ahụ, o mepụtara na mixtape nke atọ nke Gunna Drip Season 3. O guzobekwara otu mmepụta ihe ndekọ ya, The Playmakers
